Palomino is equipped with two 9-foot pool tables and seven 8-foot pool tables.We host everyone from people who have never seen a pool table in their lives to serious professionals.
We have FREE pool from open to close on Tuesdays & Wednesdays, and host an
in-house pool league on Thursdays. Not into billiards? We are also just a fun place to hang! We have a full bar, plenty of space to hang with buds, a photobooth, and a stage where we host DJ's and live music from time to time. We are also connected to
The Backyard
bar & venue and
Boca Fiesta
restaurant!
​
Palomino has a well-stocked, full liquor bar and pride ourselves on (hopefully) being able to accommodate most anyone's taste! We use fresh produce in our drinks and juice our lemons and limes daily for cocktails and our house-made sour mix.
With our wide range of ingredients, we can usually make your desired drink, shot or cocktail! Can't decide? We offer a short cocktail list with our house takes on classics like mojitos, old fashioneds, caipirianhas, pimm's cups, and more!
​
We have a great selection of beers, seltzers, and ciders ranging from local breweries (
Swamphead
,
First Magnitude
,
Cypress & Grove
, etc.) to the big name domestic
and import classics.
​
We also offer a good selection of non-alcoholic options including NA beers, craft sodas, local cold-brew coffee by
Opus
, ginger beer, coke products, juices, red bull, Gatorade and more!
​
COME HANG!
